collection.description: Matrix World is an open world that enables users to build 3D immersive applications on top of several blockchains. In Matrix World, users can take advantage of traditional 3D open-world features such as building 3D architectures, hosting virtual meetings, exhibiting NFTs, and more advanced functionality such as creating their own 3D decentralized applications (DApps) using Matrix's built-in computational resources. https://matrixworld.org/home
